          <p class='first-para'>
            rose to move that the Grand Committee do report to the House that it has considered the Pension Protection Fund (PPF Ombudsman) Order 2005. <span class="italic">[8th Report from the Joint Committee]</span></p><p>
            The noble Baroness said: I hope that it will be for the convenience of the Grand Committee and with the consent of Members opposite that we take all four measures together, rather than seek to make separate speeches on each.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
